quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,Nditsuba khuliuba nende obulafu bwalio
  91,2,"Nende\tkhumwesi\tshingala kuliloondanga"
  91,3,Nende khushitere olwashiliretsanga habulafu
  91,4,Nende eshilo olwa shifunikhanga
  91,5,"Nende\tkhulikulu\tnende\tulia waliumbakha"
  91,6,Nende khuliloba nende ulia walikwalasia
  91,7,"Nende\tkhu mwoyo nende ulia wakuleng’aasia"
  91,8,Mana nakumanyisia injila yamabii nende yamalayi. 15. Naye sharitsanga karulilaho tawe
  91,9,toto bwene yamala okhubura ulwa wakutswenula
  91,10,Ne toto bwene yamala okhusikha ulia wakulekhula
  91,11,babu Tsamudi bayingasia (omurumwa wabu) khulwo okhubeela obufuru bwabu
  91,12,ulwa yanguya womwoyo omumu mubo
  91,13,"aho Omurumwa wa Nyasaye nababoolela mbu ; ingamia ino ni ya Nyasaye, muyileshe inywe amatsi kayio ne mulayira tawe"
  91,14,"Mana bamala bamuyingasia nibaiyira, khulwako Nyasaye wabu nabasishia khulwo khubeela tsimbi tsiabu nabamala boosi"
  91,15,Naye sharitsanga karulilaho tawe